title: Club Problem
body: i made my club in in it but it wont show in my club spot

replies.body:
Hmm.. we'll need to look into some things to see if we can resolve this together. If you could hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) with the club name and tag (if you made one) then we can assist you further.
